<h1>All-in-One Web Toolkit</h1>
<br>
<br>
The All-in-One Web Toolkit is a comprehensive web-based platform that provides multiple utilities in a single interface, including PDF tools, image tools, and text-based tools. The goal of this project is to simplify everyday digital tasks by offering a user-friendly and efficient solution without requiring users to install multiple applications.
<br>
<br>
The platform includes features such as PDF merging, splitting, signing, and conversion, along with image compression, resizing, format conversion, and watermarking. It also integrates smart tools like a JSON formatter, text utilities, and AI-based features such as summarization, plagiarism checking, and content enhancement.
<br>
<br>
Built using modern web technologies like HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and relevant libraries, the application focuses on performance, responsiveness, and client-side processing to ensure data privacy and fast execution.
<br>
<br>
This project demonstrates strong front-end development skills, problem-solving ability, and the integration of multiple functionalities into a single scalable platform.
